					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3">
					<h4 class="d-none d-sm-block">加微信免费领POS机</h4>
					<div class="qrcode-link">
						<img src="~/images/wechat.jpg" style="width: 150px;" />
